	(text_box "Use cases:\n\nSWD with SWO:\nJumper J3 for SWO and J4 for ~{RESET}.\n\nSWD with UART debug output:\nJumper J3 for JLinkRX, and J4 for ~{RESET}.  The JLink debuggers can be configured to support a USB CDC ACM serial port.\n\nSWD with bi-directional UART:\nJumper J3 for JLinkRX and J4 for JLinkTX.  Reset is not connected.\n\nJTAG:\nJumper J3 for SWO (TDO) and J4 for JLinkTX (TDI).  SWDIO becomes TMS, and SWCLK becomes TCLK. Neither Reset nor TRST are connected.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 53.34 25.4 0)
		(size 34.29 48.26)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
